<h2 id="1000">13. Viewing the API log</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>Data » API log</strong> menu contains a history of processes that run via the bol.com interface.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Viewing the API log:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Data » API log » Tab: API log</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the format <strong>bol.com</strong> from the <strong>Process</strong> drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a <strong>date</strong> if you only want to see entries for a specific day.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) to carry out the search.<br>
→ The processes are displayed.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
